										<width>42540</width>
									</dimensions>
								</extent>
								<collation>
									<p>95 membranes, with wooden roller (662mm long). </p>
								</collation>
								<condition>
									<p>One liquid spill. </p>
									<p>A few cuts/tears at edges. </p>
									<p>Some erasures. Slight dirt. </p>
									<p>Pleats and folds (not obscuring text). </p>
								</condition>
							</supportDesc>
							<layoutDesc>
								<layout columns="239" ruledLines="49" writtenLines="49">
									<p>Uniform layout. </p>
									<p>Ruling by hard point.</p>
									<p>239 columns in total, one to five columns per membrane. </p>
									<p>No tagin. </p>
									<p>No majuscular and minuscular letters, or special shapes of letters. </p>
									<p>The &quot;puncta extraordinaria&quot; placed on a few words only. </p>
								</layout>
